Title: LIVE PODCAST: Snake Oil Comics
Presenters: Travis McIntire, Devin Foether, Stephen Sharar
Book Description: 'Snake Oil Comics is a comics and nerd lifestyle podcast recorded live from Coy's Comics in Saginaw- MI. Hosts Travis McIntire- Devin Foether- and Jason Lloyd strive to support the industry they love by interviewing independent comic creators- talking about significant comic story lines or characters- and getting a comic shop owner's perspective on what's hot and what's not. '
